Resource Moniter : 
1. Resource moniter can track single VWH or group of VWH or entire snowflake account
2. You can create multiple resource moniter to moniter and manage credit usage at different level
3. RM(Resource moniter) at account level can't control credit usage by serverless features - Snowpipe, Automatic Reclustering, Materialize view  
4. If a RM moniters a VWH, another RM can't moniter the same VWH
5. Only AccountAdmin create Resource moniter

Information_Schema is created automatically  for every snowflake DB. It provides metadata information on the objects created in the DB
Last 365 days history of warehouse credit usage - WAREHOUSE_METERING_HISTORY.ACCOUNT_USAGE
Data is kept for 365 days in ACCOUNT_USAGE schema
